pack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3zc","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":7432,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/02\/cats-wudu-taharah-halal\/","url_meta":{"origin":13714,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Cats: Cats not impure, do not nullify ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, cats are not impure, as they meander around you.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"It is the majority opinion of the scholars among the companions of the Prophet (s\u0323), the successors, and those after them such as Al-Shafi'i,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-sireen-degrades-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":13714,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Sireen on Sahaba: Whoever degrades Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ayyub reported: Muhammad ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI suspect that a man who denigrates Abu Bakr and Umar does not love the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3685 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Schola